        "## Feature Engineering\n",
        "\n",
        "### Subtask:\n",
        "Create new features to enhance predictive power: calculate 'FamilySize' (SibSp + Parch + 1), derive 'IsAlone' (binary based on FamilySize), and extract 'Title' from the 'Name' column, simplifying titles by grouping rare ones into broader categories.\n"
      ]
